# Introduction

Script to automate some initial setup steps.

Will set up:

- User configured in USERNAME
- Add public key configured in PUBKEY
- Disable root login
- Add ssh-rsa so login with vscode will work
- Add github ssh host config to ssh config file

## Howto

Copy the env.example file to env and fill in the USERNAME and PUBKEY parameters.

Run `./setup.sh` 
